          "reviewBody": "SV High School is always clean, good and colorful environment.\nTeachers and employees are very much responsible, polite and doing the friendly interaction with parents.\nCurriculum also good for kindergarten, my son is learning different things everyday.\nSports, Music and other activities also good, I am really very much satisfied with SV High school, Vanagaram",
