          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Joined my daughter keerthy sankar here...first thing is hats off to their(deciding authority) team for deciding such beautiful uniform....attrcative polo tshirt as top and dark colour skirt..The school has actually sent a strong msg that \"they care for my daughter\" is what I understood from their uniform choice... infrastructure is good and they have lot of plans in developing the facility(sports)since I spoke to correspondent mam,she was so clear and confident about the future plans of the school...Special mention to all the staffs, especially the bus manager...he is so perfect in handling parents and the bus staff...i was intially scared to send my duaghter to school in bus but i made up my mind after speaking the bus manager..hoping for the roads to get better(worst roads).All the very Best SV high school ..we as parents will always standby the school and it's plans..Impressive and developing...",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
