            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A great place for kids to create memories while getting a chance to learn in a world class environment.\nSV High school offers a unique combination of traditional values and high infrastructure standards.\nThe school is built on a long heritage of educational experience of the Sri Venkateswara Educational Institutions.\nOverall a great place to put kids in and explore a holistic world of education.",
          "publisher": {
