            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Great school with good staff and ample space in the class and ground. High quality teaching with advanced syllabus. The teacher's are very supportive and attend to students if they have doubt immediately. We can expect students to come in high ranks by the coaching given in this school. As the teaching is interactive and mental learning the students don't have to carry the work to home. The school takes care of all studying work what all parents will like. Highly recommended in the surrounding area.",
